{"tid":45836,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解道可道，非常道？","createTime":"2016-12-19T08:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T16:47:52.000Z","uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5357580d4c1984b5f6308cc8e9c6a38ff4c6e96","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解講得出黎嘅道，就唔係永恆嘅道？"},{"pid":"9d5ff2112fc9b151b4a02d9ce26498c0fa688b3b","tid":45836,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"道可盜，非常盜"},{"pid":"349ecd74475b6c0aca415e5716353f0c7e92acab","tid":45836,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"每次睇到呢句 我都會諗起荀卿篇解蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故為蔽：欲為蔽，惡為蔽，始為蔽，終為蔽，遠為蔽，近為蔽，博為蔽，淺為蔽，古為蔽，今為蔽。凡萬物異則莫不相為蔽，此心術之公患也。<br />\n<br />\n點講都係蔽於一曲而闇於大理<br />\n所以道可道就唔係真正嘅大道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f7d787eaa543a6d2951eec2beaeb7373374d5c","tid":45836,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"我 pay pay pay pay lay"},{"pid":"47c6c25631c53ec822778165f4a80f8c1b9f2653","tid":45836,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"你手口, 永遠唔會準確表達到你嘅思想, 咁上下"},{"pid":"3c67ec1404a96feb7a1810e2cb813cdd26ea9676","tid":45836,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"天道地道，人道我道<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"5d138d387d716e7c646adfb202d96f93705a6a85","tid":45836,"uid":53632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"道理是不能被準確表達的，但我又想你知，我唔講你又唔會知，所以就要帶左頭盔先"},{"pid":"c2f0c4c5b1916251303c262a826b99d01f4c0002","tid":45836,"uid":2414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天道地道，人道我道<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c6234cb5fd78bde08ee528fd8c93e9214de298","tid":45836,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"正如數學家討論既圓, 永遠唔係佢畫係黑板上果個<br />\n不過柏拉圖果套食左屎好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4c45ba35b8027ebcb721c69f3e0ffa3e625ec2","tid":45836,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"我自求我道！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99794c6f2c5532fbdf07f09950aced9e281150e","tid":45836,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"語言本身係一種限制，將一件整體事物拆散左。<br />\n<br />\n譬如蘋果咁，當我提及「蘋果」嘅時候，你嘅腦海通常只係浮現左蘋果嘅外型，但係蘋果肉同果核呢？佢地都係蘋果嘅一部分黎，人好少會將一舊蘋果裏裏外外都想像到出黎，至多係諗到舊切開左嘅蘋果。但係切開左嘅蘋果同完整嘅蘋果已經係兩回事啦。<br />\n<br />\n所以話道係可以講，只不過你講極都只係道嘅某一部分，而唔係道嘅整體"},{"pid":"3b70c5c58195011ecfca158eea5696d150eced54","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道可盜，非常盜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9388559bb96031ec1dc2c94b0d6e2582abb278b9","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次睇到呢句 我都會諗起荀卿篇解蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故為蔽：欲為蔽，惡為蔽，始為蔽，終為蔽，遠為蔽，近為蔽，博為蔽，淺為蔽，古為蔽，今為蔽。凡萬物異則莫不相為蔽，此心術之公患也。<br />\n<br />\n點講都係蔽於一曲而闇於大理<br />\n所以道可道就唔係真正嘅大道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n道德經入面老子用「小」去形容道本體，但用「大」形容道嘅作用。大道係隱蔽、微小。「蔽」一字同上面荀子一篇未見有直接關係<br />\n<br />\n「視之不見，名曰夷；聽之不聞，名曰希；搏之不得，名曰微。.....<br />\n執古之道，以御今之有。能知古始，是謂道紀。」<br />\n<br />\n「......保此道者不欲盈。夫唯不盈，故能蔽而新成。」<br />\n<br />\n但荀子「蔽於一曲」個句又有道可道非常道嘅精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f6d9c062a7ca0640268f2c85ce6faccdd9341b","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你手口, 永遠唔會準確表達到你嘅思想, 咁上下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Why? 咁樣用文字/數式得唔得？"},{"pid":"adc78048389a1844190d24722a9726608b00027d","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正如數學家討論既圓, 永遠唔係佢畫係黑板上果個<br />\n不過柏拉圖果套食左屎好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n圓可圓，非常圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7338768ba3321e265d1080f0524aa23383cd344","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>語言本身係一種限制，將一件整體事物拆散左。<br />\n<br />\n譬如蘋果咁，當我提及「蘋果」嘅時候，你嘅腦海通常只係浮現左蘋果嘅外型，但係蘋果肉同果核呢？佢地都係蘋果嘅一部分黎，人好少會將一舊蘋果裏裏外外都想像到出黎，至多係諗到舊切開左嘅蘋果。但係切開左嘅蘋果同完整嘅蘋果已經係兩回事啦。<br />\n<br />\n所以話道係可以講，只不過你講極都只係道嘅某一部分，而唔係道嘅整體</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 名可名非常名，蘋果又叫林擒，又叫 Apple"},{"pid":"5580cd5c80b57f49672bc83bf1545e370f0901d3","tid":45836,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"天之道，損有餘而補不足"},{"pid":"10a05f32366e59da1d103c271a8f116c18c9b53c","tid":45836,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天之道，損有餘而補不足</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b82477c332c0ee1a1657f15b28f6cb430a87540","tid":45836,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"就好似&pi;既實數一樣 無論講幾多個小數位 都同真實既&pi;有相差"},{"pid":"11d98f11df71dd94ea71a908cd854f6b6b7f31e0","tid":45836,"uid":46038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天之道，損有餘而補不足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是故虛勝實，不足勝有餘"},{"pid":"dd6ffd1851e2ed93ad363f2325d539d0fb9a480b","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天之道，損有餘而補不足</blockquote><br />\n「因為凡是有的，還要賜給他，使他豐足有餘；凡是沒有的，連他有的也將從他那裡被拿走。」馬太福音 13：12<br />\n<br />\n「天之道，其猶張弓與！高者抑之，下者舉之；有餘者損之，不足者補之。天之道，損有餘而補不足；人之道，則不然，損不足以奉有餘。」天道章 77<br />\n<br />\n你提起呢一章我諗起基督教嘅呢一句「金句」，將聖經同道德經拍埋，高下立見。聖經所謂嘅神嘅道係道德經入面並非天之道，反而係人之道。雖然否定唔到神嘅存在，但至少由呢個角度出發，基督教嘅神其實帶有人嘅本性，所以，如果基督教嘅神係存在，神唔止按照自己個樣創造人，仲按照自己嘅性格創造人。神都被自然所規限"},{"pid":"dd40900c94728dc11bcf01066dba1f6cccda070d","tid":45836,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就好似&pi;既實數一樣 無論講幾多個小數位 都同真實既&pi;有相差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6cf45100776a4c069f36a2539583c8e744070d","tid":45836,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"409cd71ea625156666d184455d39ea068b743383","tid":45836,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天之道，損有餘而補不足</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa57aef42d157b4649b80eca690c8f1d5a12819","tid":45836,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每次睇到呢句 我都會諗起荀卿篇解蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故為蔽：欲為蔽，惡為蔽，始為蔽，終為蔽，遠為蔽，近為蔽，博為蔽，淺為蔽，古為蔽，今為蔽。凡萬物異則莫不相為蔽，此心術之公患也。<br />\n<br />\n點講都係蔽於一曲而闇於大理<br />\n所以道可道就唔係真正嘅大道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n道德經入面老子用「小」去形容道本體，但用「大」形容道嘅作用。大道係隱蔽、微小。「蔽」一字同上面荀子一篇未見有直接關係<br />\n<br />\n「視之不見，名曰夷；聽之不聞，名曰希；搏之不得，名曰微。.....<br />\n執古之道，以御今之有。能知古始，是謂道紀。」<br />\n<br />\n「......保此道者不欲盈。夫唯不盈，故能蔽而新成。」<br />\n<br />\n但荀子「蔽於一曲」個句又有道可道非常道嘅精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係無關係嘅<br />\n因為荀卿講蔽於一曲而闇於大理係客觀會因為好多野而演變成偏見<br />\n變咗偏見就唔再係事物嘅真正道理<br />\n正如天有常 不為堯存桀亡<br />\n以後暴君在位會亂天道都係蔽<br />\n<br />\n道德經嘅道比較近於自然之道<br />\n而道嘅實質內容就係無<br />\n無為就係最自然之道<br />\n「可道」就唔再係「無」唔係「無」 又點會係常道<br />\n因為真正嘅道就係不可道 因為無 所以就不可道 亦都係不能道<br />\n<br />\n解蔽果個道同李耳之道我覺得都係好難真係用文字講 相似地方就係呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}